commit.message: Replaced the raw minigame and boss values with enums

Show the friendly error message even on catched exceptions
Fixed a possible crash when the index is not reset on a search field
Increased the compression level of the GHA artifacts

Updated the GitHub Actions tasks due to GitHub warning

It's pretty ridiculous, but whatever.
Show the Git revision info in the title bar

Fixed a type conversion warning
